      <title>《Starfield》和《夺宝奇兵》仍是 Xbox 独占游戏，但 Phil Spencer 不排除在 PS5 上发布的可能性</title>
      <link>https://www.ign.com/articles/starfield-and-indiana-jones-are-still-xbox-exclusives-but-phil-spencer-doesnt-rule-out-ps5-release</link>
